<h4>Hex to binary conversion examples</h4>
<ul>
<li>(1E3)<sub>16</sub> = (0001 1110 0011)<sub>2</sub></li> 
<li>(0A2B)<sub>16</sub> = (0000 1010 0010 1011)<sub>2</sub></li>
<li>(7E0C)<sub>16</sub> = (0111 1110 0000 1100)<sub>2</sub></li>
</ul>
